\[0.3=\delta\geq\frac{1}{3}\cdot\mathbf{Pr}_{(S_{1},S_{2},S_{3})\sim\mathcal{C}}[ S_{1}=S_{2}=S_{3}]\geq\frac{0.98}{3}>0.32\,.\]

