\[\|p-q\|_{\text{TV}}=\frac{1}{2}\sum_{i\in[n-1]}|p_{i}-q_{i}|=\frac{\alpha}{2} \sum_{i\in[n-1]}|\tilde{p}_{i}-\tilde{q}_{i}|=\alpha\cdot\|\tilde{p}-\tilde{ q}\|_{\text{TV}}.\]

